Package: omix
Type: Package
Title: Randomize Samples for -omics Profiling
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lucy Sinke
Maintainer: Lucy Sinke <l.j.sinke@lumc.nl>
Description: Optimizes distribution of randomization variables to 
    minimize correlations between them and technical covariates.
    Also allows the production of PDF sample sheets for easy
    manual pipetting of samples in the lab.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    gridExtra,
    magrittr,
    readr,
    tidyselect
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
